    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade A80 chassis powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six. This specimen retains its factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger setup with optimal boost pressure and zero shaft play. The drivetrain features the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: a recent leak-down test confirms sub-3% variance across all cylinders, and the valve train remains within factory tolerances. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, preserving the integrity of the double-wishbone suspension and original Bilstein dampers. All VIN-matching panels are present, confirming an accident-free provenance. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
