      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that serves as a virtual time capsule. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance that must be seen to be believed. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original floor mats are pristine. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule at authorized facilities. We have a comprehensive binder of every service receipt and inspection report since new. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any debris or oxidation. This is a rare opportunity to own a museum-quality example that drives as smoothly as the day it was delivered.",
